[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mA libFuzzer run terminated with an “ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout” message. The fuzzing[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprocess exceeded its allotted execution time and was stopped by the built-in [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtimeout mechanism.[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Issue overview  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  During a fuzzing session using libFuzzer, the fuzzer aborted execution after [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreaching its predefined time limit. No specific crash or memory corruption was [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreported—only a timeout.[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Vulnerability type  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Although no explicit vulnerability [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., buffer overflow[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is indicated, the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtimeout suggests a performance or liveness issue in the code under test [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfor [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexample, a long-running loop or blocking operation[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Key observations and findings  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The timeout was triggered by libFuzzer’s watchdog timer rather than by a [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msanitizer failure or crash handler.  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The fuzzer harness served solely as an entry point; it did not itself produce [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe timeout.  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Inputs generated by the fuzzer caused the target code to exceed expected [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexecution time.[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Areas of the codebase to investigate  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The fuzzing harness: review how it invokes target functions and whether it [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39menforces its own time or iteration limits.  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Core libraries or functions under test: identify loops, recursive calls, or [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mblocking I/O operations that could lead to extended execution paths.  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • External dependencies or resources: check for network, file, or synchronization[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprimitives that might stall or wait indefinitely.  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Timeout configuration: examine libFuzzer’s flag settings [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., ‑timeout[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconfirm threshold values and ensure they align with expected performance [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcharacteristics.[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m75[0m[39m:    public static void [0m[1;35msetMinInflateRatio[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdouble ratio[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                        [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m77[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m78[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m79[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m80[0m[39m:     * Returns the current minimum compression rate that is used.[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m81[0m[39m:     *[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m82[0m[39m:     * See [0m[1;35msetMinInflateRatio[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m for details.[0m                                     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m85[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m86[0m[39m:    public static double [0m[1;35mgetMinInflateRatio[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m91[0m[39m:     * Returns the current maximum file count that is used.[0m                      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m93[0m[39m:     * See [0m[1;35msetMaxFileCount[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m for details.[0m                                        [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m95[0m[39m:     * @return The max accepted file count [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi.e. the max number of files we [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mallow inside zip files that we read - including OOXML files like xlsx, docx, pptx, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39metc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m96[0m[39m:     * @since POI [0m[1;36m5.2[0m[39m.[0m[1;36m4[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m97[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m98[0m[39m:    public static long [0m[1;35mgetMaxFileCount[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m99[0m[39m:        return MAX_FILE_COUNT;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m100[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m101[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m102[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m103[0m[39m:     * Sets the maximum file count that we allow inside zip files that we read [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m104[0m[39m:     * including OOXML files like xlsx, docx, pptx, etc. The default is [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m105[0m[39m:     *[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m106[0m[39m:     * @param maxFileCount The max accepted file count[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m107[0m[39m:     * @since POI [0m[1;36m5.2[0m[39m.[0m[1;36m4[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m108[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m109[0m[39m:    public static void [0m[1;35msetMaxFileCount[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfinal long maxFileCount[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m110[0m[39m:        MAX_FILE_COUNT = maxFileCount;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m111[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m112[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m113[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m114[0m[39m:     * Sets the maximum file size of a single zip entry. It defaults to 4GB,[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m115[0m[39m:     * i.e. the [0m[1;36m32[0m[39m-bit zip format maximum.[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m116[0m[39m:     *[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m117[0m[39m:     * This can be used to limit memory consumption and protect against[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m118[0m[39m:     * security vulnerabilities when documents are provided by users.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m119[0m[39m:     *[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m120[0m[39m:     * @param maxEntrySize the max. file size of a single zip entry[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m121[0m[39m:     * @throws IllegalArgumentException for negative maxEntrySize[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m122[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m123[0m[39m:    public static void [0m[1;35msetMaxEntrySize[0m[1;39m([0m[39mlong maxEntrySize[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m124[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmaxEntrySize < [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m125[0m[39m:            throw new [0m[1;35mIllegalArgumentException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Max entry size must be greater [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mthan or equal to zero"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m126[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmaxEntrySize > DEFAULT_MAX_ENTRY_SIZE[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m127[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mLOG.warn[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"setting max entry size greater than 4Gb can be risky; set[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mto [0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m bytes"[0m[39m, maxEntrySize[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m128[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m129[0m[39m:        MAX_ENTRY_SIZE = maxEntrySize;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m130[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m131[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m132[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m133[0m[39m:     * Returns the current maximum allowed uncompressed file size.[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m134[0m[39m:     *[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m135[0m[39m:     * See [0m[1;35msetMaxEntrySize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m for details.[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m136[0m[39m:     *[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m138[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m139[0m[39m:    public static long [0m[1;35mgetMaxEntrySize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m140[0m[39m:        return MAX_ENTRY_SIZE;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m141[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m142[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m143[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m144[0m[39m:     * Sets the grace entry size of a single zip entry. It defaults to 100Kb.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m145[0m[39m:     *[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m146[0m[39m:     * When decompressed data in a zip entry is smaller than this size, the[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m147[0m[39m:     * Minimum Inflation Ratio check is ignored.[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m148[0m[39m:     *[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m149[0m[39m:     * Setting this to a very small value may lead to more files being flagged[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m150[0m[39m:     * as potential Zip Bombs are rejected as a result.[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m151[0m[39m:     *[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m152[0m[39m:     * @param graceEntrySize the grace entry size of a single zip entry[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m153[0m[39m:     * @throws IllegalArgumentException for negative graceEntrySize[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m154[0m[39m:     * @since POI [0m[1;36m5.2[0m[39m.[0m[1;36m4[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m155[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m156[0m[39m:    public static void [0m[1;35msetGraceEntrySize[0m[1;39m([0m[39mlong graceEntrySize[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m157[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mgraceEntrySize < [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m158[0m[39m:            throw new [0m[1;35mIllegalArgumentException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Grace entry size must be [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mgreater than or equal to zero"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m159[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m160[0m[39m:        GRACE_ENTRY_SIZE = graceEntrySize;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m161[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m162[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m163[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m164[0m[39m:     * Returns the current threshold for decompressed data in zip entries that [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mare regarded as too small[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m165[0m[39m:     * to worry about from a Zip Bomb perspective [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdefault is 100Kb[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m166[0m[39m:     *[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m167[0m[39m:     * See [0m[1;35msetGraceEntrySize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m for details.[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m168[0m[39m:     *[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m169[0m[39m:     * @return The current grace entry size[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m170[0m[39m:     * @since POI [0m[1;36m5.2[0m[39m.[0m[1;36m4[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m171[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m172[0m[39m:    public static long [0m[1;35mgetGraceEntrySize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m173[0m[39m:        return GRACE_ENTRY_SIZE;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m174[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m175[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m176[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m177[0m[39m:     * Sets the maximum number of characters of text that are[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m178[0m[39m:     * extracted before an exception is thrown during extracting[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m179[0m[39m:     * text from documents.[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m180[0m[39m:     *[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m181[0m[39m:     * This can be used to limit memory consumption and protect against[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m182[0m[39m:     * security vulnerabilities when documents are provided by users.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m183[0m[39m:     *[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m184[0m[39m:     * @param maxTextSize the max. file size of a single zip entry[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m185[0m[39m:     * @throws IllegalArgumentException for negative maxTextSize[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m186[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m187[0m[39m:    public static void [0m[1;35msetMaxTextSize[0m[1;39m([0m[39mlong maxTextSize[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m188[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmaxTextSize < [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m189[0m[39m:            throw new [0m[1;35mIllegalArgumentException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Max text size must be greater [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mthan or equal to zero"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m190[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m[39melse if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmaxTextSize > DEFAULT_MAX_TEXT_SIZE[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m191[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mLOG.warn[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"setting max text size greater than [0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m can be risky; set [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mto [0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m chars"[0m[39m, DEFAULT_MAX_TEXT_SIZE, maxTextSize[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m192[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m193[0m[39m:        MAX_TEXT_SIZE = maxTextSize;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m194[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m195[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m196[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m197[0m[39m:     * Returns the current maximum allowed text size.[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m198[0m[39m:     *[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m199[0m[39m:     * @return The max accepted text size.[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m200[0m[39m:     * @see #[0m[1;35msetMaxTextSize[0m[1;39m([0m[39mlong[0m[1;39m)[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m638[0m[39m:     * If your package is open read only, then you should call [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m@link [0m          [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m648[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35misClosed[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                       [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m33[0m[39m: * Provides a way to get at all the ZipEntries[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m34[0m[39m: *  from a ZipInputStream, as many times as required.[0m                            [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m39[0m[39m: *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m40[0m[39m:public class ZipInputStreamZipEntrySource implements ZipEntrySource [0m[1;39m{[0m            [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m46[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m47[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m48[0m[39m:     * Set the threshold at which a zip entry is regarded as too large for [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mholding in memory[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m49[0m[39m:     * and the data is put in a temp file instead[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m50[0m[39m:     * @param thresholdBytes number of bytes at which a zip entry is regarded as[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtoo large for holding in memory[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m51[0m[39m:     *                       and the data is put in a temp file instead - [0m       [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m57[0m[39m:    public static void [0m[1;35msetThresholdBytesForTempFiles[0m[1;39m([0m[39mint thresholdBytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m       [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m62[0m[39m:     * Get the threshold at which a zip entry is regarded as too large for [0m      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Background & Root Cause  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  LibFuzzer timeouts arise because Apache POI’s OPCPackage parsing loops over every[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mZIP entry without bounding the iteration count when using file‐based sources [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mZipFileZipEntrySource[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. While stream‐based sources [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mZipArchiveThresholdInputStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m enforce MAX_FILE_COUNT guards, file‐based [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39menumeration [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mZipFile.getEntries[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m does not. A fuzzer‐crafted archive with [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthousands of tiny entries will drive an unbounded loop in [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mOPCPackage.getPartsImpl[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, consuming CPU until libFuzzer’s timeout fires.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Preserve Existing Logic  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  – Keep all current ZIP‐bomb protections [0m[1;39m([0m[39mMAX_ENTRY_SIZE, MIN_INFLATE_RATIO[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mintact.  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  – Use the same configurable MAX_FILE_COUNT from ZipSecureFile, so users can tune [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlimits.  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  – Maintain correct behavior for well‐formed Office documents [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwhich rarely exceed[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39ma few hundred parts[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch Location & Approach  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Modify [0m[1;35mOPCPackage.getPartsImpl[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39min [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpoi-ooxml/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/openxml4j/opc/internal/ZipPackage.java[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to: [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    a. Introduce a local counter `long entryCount = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;` before the loop over zip [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mentries.  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    b. In the loop [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfor each entry[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, increment `entryCount`.  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    c. After incrementing, check `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mentryCount > [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mZipSecureFile.getMaxFileCount[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and throw an IOException [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., “Too many ZIP [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mentries: X; limit is Y”[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m if exceeded.  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   This mirrors the guard in [0m[1;35mZipArchiveThresholdInputStream.getNextEntry[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munifying file- and stream-based entry limits.[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Detailed Steps  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  a. In ZipPackage.java, locate `private Map<…> [0m[1;35mgetPartsImpl[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` or similar method [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat fetches entries via a ZipEntrySource and loops:  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    – Before entering the enumeration [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mZipEntrySource.getEntries[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, add:  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      `long entryCount = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;`  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    – Inside the while/for loop processing each ZipArchiveEntry:  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      `entryCount++;`  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mentryCount > [0m[1;35mZipSecureFile.getMaxFileCount[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m`  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        `throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mString.format[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"ZIP archive contains too many entries[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m([0m[32m%d[0m[32m)[0m[32m, exceeding max of %d"[0m[39m, entryCount, [0m[1;35mZipSecureFile.getMaxFileCount[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`  [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m`  [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  b. Ensure that this exception is propagated up as an InvalidFormatException, to [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindicate an invalid or malicious archive. OPCPackage.open should catch this and [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwrap as InvalidFormatException.[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Error Reporting & Configurability  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  – Use [0m[1;35mZipSecureFile.getMaxFileCount[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m so existing user‐accessible setter [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;35mZipSecureFile.setMaxFileCount[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m applies equally to file‐ and stream‐based [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreads.  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  – Document in change notes that MAX_FILE_COUNT prevents timeouts by bounding part[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39menumeration, and can be increased if needed for large legitimate packages.[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Testing & Validation  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  – Add a unit test creating a dummy archive with e.g. [0m[1;36m1001[0m[39m empty files to confirm [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39man IOException upon threshold breach.  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  – Verify that a normal small XSLX file still opens successfully.  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  – Run existing test suite to ensure no regressions.[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. Rationale & Side Effects  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  – This approach enforces a hard cap on number of ZIP entries, preventing [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpathological inputs from causing unbounded CPU loops under fuzz.  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  – It preserves backward compatibility [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdefault max [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m entries[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. Very large but [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlegitimate packages may need an increased limit.  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  – By throwing an IOException, we fast‐fail evil or fuzzer‐crafted archives rather[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthan spin until timeout.  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  – No changes to harness, fuzz logic, or external libraries. Only core parsing [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlogic is adjusted.[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m8[0m[39m. Reference Patterns  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  – Stream‐based guard in [0m[1;35mZipArchiveThresholdInputStream.getNextEntry[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m uses [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexactly this pattern for MAX_FILE_COUNT. Replicating it in file‐based enumeration [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mensures consistent protection.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcode_range: [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpoi-ooxml/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/openxml4j/opc/internal/ZipPackage.java:XXX-Y[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mYY  [0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         IOException [1m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        long entryCount = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         for [0m[1;39m([0m[39m;;[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mzipEntry == null[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 break;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            entryCount++;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mentryCount > maxCount[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                throw new [0m[1;35mIllegalStateException[0m[1;39m([0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                    [0m[1;35mString.format[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"ZIP archive contains too many entries [0m[32m([0m[32m%d[0m[32m)[0m[32m, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mexceeding max of %d"[0m[39m,[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                                  entryCount, maxCount[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             String name = [0m[1;35mzipEntry.getName[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mname == null || [0m[1;35mname.isEmpty[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Patch [0m[33mResult[0m[39m===[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===[0m[33mIssue[0m[39m===[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fuzzer run against the Apache POI OOXML codebase is failing with a “ERROR: [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibFuzzer: timeout” message, indicating the target code is hanging or running too [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mslowly under fuzz input. In response, a patch was proposed in [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mZipFileZipEntrySource.getEntries[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, wrapping the underlying [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mzipArchive.getEntries[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` Enumeration in a decorator that counts entries and throws[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39man `IllegalStateException` when the count exceeds [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mZipSecureFile.getMaxFileCount[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`. After applying this patch, the fuzzer still [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreports the same timeout error, and no new exception is observed.[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Initial Issue  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The fuzzer’s harness invokes POI’s OOXML ZIP-processing code and ultimately [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreports a libFuzzer timeout.  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No stack trace or exception is shown, only the generic timeout message.  [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This suggests either an infinite loop or a very slow code path during ZIP [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mentry enumeration or processing.[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Key Observations  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The timeout occurs before any visible exception, meaning the instrumentation [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdid not trigger the newly introduced `IllegalStateException`.  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The harness code itself simply drives the POI API; it is not modified and is [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39massumed not to be the root cause.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - ZIP entry enumeration [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;35mzipArchive.getEntries[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is a likely hotspot, as it [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcan yield a large or malformed stream of entries.[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch Attempt  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - File modified: [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`poi-ooxml/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/openxml4j/util/ZipFileZipEntrySource.java` [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Original method:[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     public Enumeration<? extends ZipArchiveEntry> [0m[1;35mgetEntries[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mzipArchive == null[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             throw new [0m[1;35mIllegalStateException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Zip File is closed"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         return [0m[1;35mzipArchive.getEntries[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Patched method wraps the returned `Enumeration<? extends ZipArchiveEntry>` in [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39man anonymous implementation that:[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Maintains a long `entryCount` initialized to [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m.  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • On each `[0m[1;35mnextElement[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` call, increments `entryCount`.  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • If `entryCount` exceeds `[0m[1;35mZipSecureFile.getMaxFileCount[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, throws  [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       `IllegalStateException` with a message containing both counts.  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The `[0m[1;35mhasMoreElements[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method delegates directly to the base enumeration.[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Result of Patch  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - After rebuilding and rerunning the fuzzer, it again reports “ERROR: libFuzzer:[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtimeout.”  [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No `IllegalStateException` is observed in the logs, indicating that either the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39menumeration never proceeds far enough to exceed the limit or the hang occurs [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39melsewhere.[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Areas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The default value returned by `[0m[1;35mZipSecureFile.getMaxFileCount[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` versus the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnumber of entries produced by `[0m[1;35mzipArchive.getEntries[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The behavior of `[0m[1;35mzipArchive.getEntries[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` under malformed or deeply nested ZIP[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minput — possible internal buffering or infinite iteration.  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Downstream code consuming these entries [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., code that reads entry contents,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhandles streams or recursive entry processing[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Performance characteristics and potential blocking in other parts of the OOXML[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mZIP utility classes.  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The harness’s iteration strategy and whether it exhausts the Enumeration or [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mgets stuck awaiting additional elements.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Any interaction between the fuzzer’s timeout settings and lengthy I/O or [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomputational work in POI’s ZIP handling.[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mNo root-cause diagnosis or mitigation steps are provided here; this report focuses [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msolely on summarizing the issue, the patch attempt, and pointers for deeper code [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minspection.[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mHere is the initial issue log of the codebase:[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<issue>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95missue[0m[39m>[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Additional Issue Log[0m                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<additional_issue>[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m54[0m[39m:            throw new [0m[1;35mIllegalStateException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Zip File is closed"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m               [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m57[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Issue Analysis and Root Cause  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The existing patch wraps only the `[0m[1;35mZipFileZipEntrySource.getEntries[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` path [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mused for file‐based ZIPs[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m with an entry‐count guard.  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The fuzzer is triggering the *stream‐based* code path [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`ZipInputStreamZipEntrySource`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, which eagerly reads all entries in its [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconstructor via an unbounded `[0m[1;35mfor[0m[1;39m([0m[39m;;[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` loop calling `[0m[1;35minp.getNextEntry[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Because there is no entry‐count check in that loop, a deeply nested or [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmalformed ZIP stream can either hang [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnever returning `null`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m or loop far beyond [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39macceptable limits, causing the libFuzzer timeout.  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Strategy to Fix  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   A. **Patch `ZipInputStreamZipEntrySource` Constructor**  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Introduce a local `long entryCount = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m` and retrieve the global threshold [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvia `[0m[1;35mZipSecureFile.getMaxFileCount[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Inside the loop, immediately after checking for `zipEntry == null`, [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mincrement `entryCount`.  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - If `entryCount` exceeds the maximum, throw an `IllegalStateException` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mto [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmatch the file‐based code path[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m with a message like:  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         `[0m[32m"ZIP archive contains too many entries [0m[32m([0m[32m<actual>[0m[32m)[0m[32m, exceeding max of [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m<threshold>"[0m[39m`.  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - This will cause the constructor to abort early on malicious or extremely [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlarge input, bubbling up the exception instead of hanging.  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   B. **Preserve Existing File‐Based Behavior**  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Leave the existing decorator in `[0m[1;35mZipFileZipEntrySource.getEntries[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mplace, so file‐based ZIPs continue to be guarded at enumeration time.  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   C. **Testing and Validation**  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Run the fuzzer again to confirm that, for oversized or pathological [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstreams, an immediate `IllegalStateException` is thrown [0m[1;39m([0m[39mvisible in the harness [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlog[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m rather than a timeout.  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Verify that standard OOXML test suites [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwith typical entry counts < [0m[1;36m1000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstill pass without change.  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Implementation Steps [0m[1;39m([0m[39mHigh-Level[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Open [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`poi-ooxml/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/openxml4j/util/ZipInputStreamZipEntrySource[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m.java`.  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Just inside the constructor, before the `[0m[1;35mfor[0m[1;39m([0m[39m;;[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` loop, declare:  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        `long entryCount = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;`  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In the loop body, after retrieving `zipEntry` and before processing its name: [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        entryCount++;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mentryCount > [0m[1;35mZipSecureFile.getMaxFileCount[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            throw new [0m[1;35mIllegalStateException[0m[1;39m([0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[1;35mString.format[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"ZIP archive contains too many entries [0m[32m([0m[32m%d[0m[32m)[0m[32m, [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mexceeding max of %d"[0m[39m,[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                              entryCount, [0m[1;35mZipSecureFile.getMaxFileCount[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Rebuild and rerun the fuzzer to confirm resolution.  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Justification  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - By placing the same guard logic in the *stream‐based* constructor, we cover [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe missing code path that was previously unprotected.  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The exception type [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`IllegalStateException`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and messaging mirror the [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfile‐based solution, ensuring consistent behavior and easy detection by the fuzzer [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mharness.  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This approach leaves all other functionality [0m[1;39m([0m[39mduplicate‐name checks, [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcontent‐loading, downstream `[0m[1;35mgetEntries[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` enumeration[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m intact, minimizing side [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39meffects and preserving existing tests.  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Any legitimate ZIP with fewer entries than `[0m[1;35mZipSecureFile.getMaxFileCount[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcontinues to work unchanged, and users may adjust the threshold via [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mZipSecureFile.setMaxFileCount[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` if needed.  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No harness or external library code is modified, and all existing tests and [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfuzzing logic remain valid.  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
